In this article, Vice President Mike Pence is interviewed about the tragic events of the Las Vegas shooting. He expresses his shock and sadness over the incident and praises the courage and selflessness of the American people. Pence emphasizes the importance of faith and unity in overcoming such challenges. He also reassures the country music community that the government will support the victims and their families, as well as investigate the incident thoroughly. Pence concludes by expressing his belief that America will emerge stronger from this tragedy.